        <h3 class='process-head'>Mini Update</h3>
        <p>
            As important as letting visitors know a little about me, I noticed how wordy things were starting to get.
            After running some unofficial interviews, it was clear that I needed to present the information in fewer words and in a more attractive package.
            It was a great opportunity to include some icons and break up my content a little to let it breathe. 
        </p>
        <p>
            I wasn't thrilled with how the ext wrapped around my photo, so I decided it was cleaner to separate the content with a border, as well.
            This made the mobile responsiveness more seamless, as well.
        </p>
