            As for text effects, there were two different types that I wanted to implement. 
            In this main navigation section, I thought it would be great to give a sense of my general philosophy when it comes to User Experience Design. 
            Using JQuery, I inserted an effect to simulate deleting and replacing text to indicate my desire to bring more humanity into my designs
        </p>
        <p>
            The second text effect I decided to implement in the resume section
            I wanted to give the impression of the constant growth and the building of skills. 
            The fade-in effect is perfect for that visualization.
            Along with this effect, I cleaned up the text of this section to showcase more of my top-level background.
        </p>
