        <h3 class='process-head'>Reflection</h3>
        <p>
            I am extremely happy with my updates to my portfolio site. 
            In terms of overall experience, not only were improvements made on a functional level (e.g. the image gallery having a more intuitive navigation), adding extra content and rearranging sections made things cleaner and more complete. 
            With the additional animations and features, the website is firing on all cylinders.
        </p>
        <p>
            Naturally with any project, there are already features I’m thinking of adding to improve the site some more. 
            While I like the cleanliness of less text in the portfolio section, adding hover captions over the images could prove beneficial. 
            Additionally, as I work on more projects, I intend to stay on top of writing thorough process articles. 
        </p>
